::Feline::

She smiled and sipped her drink. Actually, the drink felt good going 
down and she downed the whole glass.  She smiled at HotRod. 

::KitKat::

She trembled for a bit. She came around for a little bit.  She opened 
her eyes and saw Drillbit.  She gave a week smile before passing out 
again. Her body shook, then went back into stasis lock.  She was 
dying.
